( Sorry to disappoint you FIRE FOX, but Dinobot's outside now. He's firing 
at Scourge.)

* Dinobot snarled as he readied himself for Scourge's reaction to his 
assault, in a way something seemed to be missing.
He pondered the thought for a few nano-clicks when the answer came to him, 
Tavatron wasn't there fighting alongside him. He growled and took a step 
forward, it almost seemed to feel like standing out in the open with no 
armor on without Tavatron to back him up.
Dinobot growled, as long as she was in the Ark he wasn't sure if she was 
alright or not and that fact disturbed him. Why, he had no idea.
He growled, Tavatron was the only bot that he trusted to watch his back.
Dinobot shook his head and looked in Scourge's direction, but this wasn't 
time to worry about that now. He was there and fighting for not only his own 
life but Tavatron's and everybot else's as well.
He aimed his rifle at Scourge but then targeted Tankoor and fired, a mirage 
of charges headed for the tankbot as well. He couldn't even bare to think 
about what the Predacons would do to the bot's inside if they ever got in, 
even what they would do to Tavatron!
Dinobot growled, they MUST NOT get inside!!!*
